emn details recrod rakhte hobe

Idea ta darun bondhu! Ekdom professional tracker er moto hobe. Tumi je field gula chaile oigula shoho ami aro koyekta useful field add kore dicchi (jemon Resume Version - kon CV ta diye apply korecho, ar Notes).

Amra 2 ta dhap e kaj ta korbo:

Database Schema Update (Notun field gular jonno).

Frontend Update (Navbar, Table, Search, ar Details Modal).

Cholo suru kori! ЁЯЫая╕П

Dhap 1: Database Model Update (src/models/Job.js)
Prothome database ke bolte hobe je amra aro beshi tottho rakhte chai.

Tomar src/models/Job.js file er puro code muche nicher ta paste koro:

JavaScript
import mongoose from 'mongoose';

const JobSchema = new mongoose.Schema({
  // Basic Info
  title: { type: String, required: true },
  company: { type: String, required: true },
  postLink: { type: String }, // Job Post Link
  platform: { type: String, default: 'LinkedIn' }, // LinkedIn, BDJobs etc.
  location: { type: String },
  description: { type: String }, // Short summary

  // Application Details
  applicationDate: { type: Date, default: Date.now },
  status: {
    type: String,
    enum: ['Applied', 'Screening', 'Interview', 'Offer', 'Rejected'],
    default: 'Applied',
  },
  salaryExpectation: { type: String },
  
  // Contact & HR Info
  contactPerson: { type: String }, // HR Name
  contactEmail: { type: String }, // Email or Phone
  
  // Interview & Feedback
  interviewDate: { type: Date },
  feedback: { type: String }, // Interview feedback or rejection reason
  
  // Extras
  notes: { type: String }, // Personal notes
  
  createdAt: { type: Date, default: Date.now },
});

export default mongoose.models.Job || mongoose.model('Job', JobSchema);
Dhap 2: Frontend UI Update (src/app/page.js)
Ekhon amra UI ta ekdom change kore felbo.

Top: Ekta sundor Navbar.

Middle: Search bar & Filter.

Main: Ekta Table jekhane short details thakbe.

Action: "View" button chaple ekta Modal (Popup) ashbe jekhane sob details thakbe.

Tomar src/app/page.js er puro code muche nicher ta paste koro:

JavaScript
"use client";
import { useState, useEffect } from "react";

export default function Home() {
  // State Management
  const [jobs, setJobs] = useState([]);
  const [filteredJobs, setFilteredJobs] = useState([]);
  const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = useState("");
  const [selectedJob, setSelectedJob] = useState(null); // Details modal er jonno
  
  // Input States
  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState("link");
  const [inputUrl, setInputUrl] = useState("");
  const [inputText, setInputText] = useState("");
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  // Initial Load
  useEffect(() => {
    fetchJobs();
  }, []);

  // Search Functionality
  useEffect(() => {
    const results = jobs.filter(job => 
      job.title.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()) ||
      job.company.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase())
    );
    setFilteredJobs(results);
  }, [searchTerm, jobs]);

  // Fetch Jobs from DB
  const fetchJobs = async () => {
    try {
      const res = await fetch("/api/jobs");
      const data = await res.json();
      if (data.success) {
        setJobs(data.data);
        setFilteredJobs(data.data);
      }
    } catch (error) {
      console.error("Error fetching jobs:", error);
    }
  };

  // Extract Data Function
  const handleExtract = async () => {
    setLoading(true);
    let payload = {};
    if (activeTab === "link") payload = { url: inputUrl };
    else if (activeTab === "text") payload = { text: inputText };

    if (Object.keys(payload).length === 0) return;

    try {
      const res = await fetch("/api/extract", {
        method: "POST",
        headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },
        body: JSON.stringify(payload),
      });
      const data = await res.json();
      
      if (data.success) {
        // Extract howar por sorasori save kore dicchi (User er suvidhar jonno)
        await handleSaveDirectly(data.data);
      } else {
        alert("Failed to extract.");
      }
    } catch (error) {
      console.error(error);
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const handleSaveDirectly = async (jobData) => {
    try {
      const res = await fetch("/api/jobs", {
        method: "POST",
        headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },
        body: JSON.stringify(jobData),
      });
      const data = await res.json();
      if (data.success) {
        alert("Job Added Successfully! ЁЯЪА");
        setInputUrl("");
        setInputText("");
        fetchJobs();
      }
    } catch (error) {
      console.error("Error saving:", error);
    }
  };

  // Status Update Function
  const updateStatus = async (id, newStatus) => {
    // Eita amra pore API te update logic add korbo, apatoto UI te dekhi
    alert(`Status changing to ${newStatus} (Backend implementation needed)`);
  };

  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen bg-[#0f172a] text-white font-sans">
      
      {/* --- NAVBAR --- */}
      <nav className="fixed top-0 w-full bg-[#1e293b]/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-700 z-50">
        <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
          <div className="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            JobHunter AI ЁЯХ╡я╕ПтАНтЩВя╕П
          </div>
          <div className="flex space-x-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">
            <a href="#" className="hover:text-white transition">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="#" className="hover:text-white transition">Analytics</a>
            <a href="#" className="hover:text-white transition">Profile</a>
          </div>
          <div className="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
            U
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <div className="pt-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        
        {/* --- INPUT SECTION (Compact Box) --- */}
        <div className="bg-[#1e293b] p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 mb-8 shadow-lg">
          <div className="flex space-x-4 mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
            <button onClick={() => setActiveTab("link")} className={`text-sm font-bold pb-1 ${activeTab === "link" ? "text-blue-400 border-b-2 border-blue-400" : "text-gray-400"}`}>ЁЯФЧ Add via Link</button>
            <button onClick={() => setActiveTab("text")} className={`text-sm font-bold pb-1 ${activeTab === "text" ? "text-blue-400 border-b-2 border-blue-400" : "text-gray-400"}`}>ЁЯУЭ Add via Text</button>
          </div>
          
          <div className="flex gap-2">
            {activeTab === "link" ? (
              <input 
                type="text" 
                placeholder="Paste Job Link..."
                className="flex-1 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 text-white text-sm focus:border-blue-500 outline-none"
                value={inputUrl}
                onChange={(e) => setInputUrl(e.target.value)}
              />
            ) : (
              <input
                type="text"
                placeholder="Paste Job Description..."
                className="flex-1 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 text-white text-sm focus:border-blue-500 outline-none"
                value={inputText}
                onChange={(e) => setInputText(e.target.value)}
              />
            )}
            <button 
              onClick={handleExtract}
              disabled={loading}
              className="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm transition"
            >
              {loading ? "..." : "Add Job тЮХ"}
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* --- SEARCH & FILTER --- */}
        <div className="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
          <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-200">All Applications ({filteredJobs.length})</h2>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Search by Company or Title..." 
            className="p-2 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm w-64 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none"
            value={searchTerm}
            onChange={(e) => setSearchTerm(e.target.value)}
          />
        </div>

        {/* --- DATA TABLE --- */}
        <div className="overflow-x-auto bg-[#1e293b] rounded-xl border border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
          <table className="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr className="bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
                <th className="p-4 border-b border-gray-700">SL</th>
                <th className="p-4 border-b border-gray-700">Date</th>
                <th className="p-4 border-b border-gray-700">Company</th>
                <th className="p-4 border-b border-gray-700">Role</th>
                <th className="p-4 border-b border-gray-700">Status</th>
                <th className="p-4 border-b border-gray-700 text-center">Actions</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody className="text-sm text-gray-300">
              {filteredJobs.map((job, index) => (
                <tr key={job._id} className="hover:bg-gray-700/50 transition border-b border-gray-700/50 last:border-0">
                  <td className="p-4">{index + 1}</td>
                  <td className="p-4">{new Date(job.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()}</td>
                  <td className="p-4 font-semibold text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                    {job.company}
                    {job.postLink && <a href={job.postLink} target="_blank" className="text-blue-400 text-xs">тЖЧ</a>}
                  </td>
                  <td className="p-4">{job.title}</td>
                  <td className="p-4">
                    <span className={`px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold 
                      ${job.status === 'Applied' ? 'bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400' : 
                        job.status === 'Interview' ? 'bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-400' : 
                        job.status === 'Rejected' ? 'bg-red-500/20 text-red-400' : 'bg-gray-600'}`}>
                      {job.status}
                    </span>
                  </td>
                  <td className="p-4 text-center">
                    <button 
                      onClick={() => setSelectedJob(job)}
                      className="text-sm bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded border border-gray-600 transition"
                    >
                      Details
                    </button>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              ))}
              {filteredJobs.length === 0 && (
                <tr>
                  <td colSpan="6" className="p-8 text-center text-gray-500">No jobs found.</td>
                </tr>
              )}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* --- DETAILS MODAL (Popup) --- */}
      {selectedJob && (
        <div className="fixed inset-0 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center z-50 p-4">
          <div className="bg-[#1e293b] w-full max-w-2xl rounded-2xl border border-gray-600 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
            
            {/* Modal Header */}
            <div className="bg-gray-800 p-6 border-b border-gray-700 flex justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-white">{selectedJob.title}</h2>
                <p className="text-blue-400 text-lg">{selectedJob.company}</p>
              </div>
              <button onClick={() => setSelectedJob(null)} className="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-2xl">&times;</button>
            </div>

            {/* Modal Body */}
            <div className="p-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-h-[70vh] overflow-y-auto">
              
              {/* Column 1 */}
              <div className="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Platform</label>
                  <p className="text-gray-300">{selectedJob.platform || "N/A"}</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Location</label>
                  <p className="text-gray-300">{selectedJob.location || "Remote"}</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Salary Expectation</label>
                  <p className="text-green-400 font-mono">{selectedJob.salaryExpectation || selectedJob.salary || "Negotiable"}</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">HR / Contact Person</label>
                  <p className="text-gray-300">{selectedJob.contactPerson || "Unknown"}</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              {/* Column 2 */}
              <div className="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Current Status</label>
                  <select className="w-full bg-gray-900 border border-gray-600 rounded p-1 mt-1 text-sm focus:border-blue-500">
                    <option>{selectedJob.status}</option>
                    <option>Interview</option>
                    <option>Offer</option>
                    <option>Rejected</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Interview Date</label>
                  <p className="text-gray-300">{selectedJob.interviewDate ? new Date(selectedJob.interviewDate).toLocaleDateString() : "Not scheduled"}</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Contact Email/Phone</label>
                  <p className="text-gray-300">{selectedJob.contactEmail || "N/A"}</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              {/* Full Width Items */}
              <div className="col-span-2 mt-2">
                <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">Job Summary / Description</label>
                <div className="bg-gray-900 p-3 rounded border border-gray-700 text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">
                  {selectedJob.description || "No description available."}
                </div>
              </div>

               <div className="col-span-2">
                <label className="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">My Feedback / Notes</label>
                <textarea 
                  className="w-full bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded p-2 mt-1 text-sm focus:border-blue-500"
                  placeholder="Write your notes here..."
                  rows="2"
                >{selectedJob.notes || ""}</textarea>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Modal Footer */}
            <div className="p-4 bg-gray-800 border-t border-gray-700 flex justify-end gap-3">
              <button onClick={() => setSelectedJob(null)} className="px-4 py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-white text-sm font-bold">Close</button>
              <button className="px-6 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">Save Changes</button>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      )}

    </div>
  );
}
Ki ki change korlam:

Schema (DB): Notun onek field add hoyeche (contactPerson, interviewDate, feedback, notes etc).

Navbar: Upore fixed JobHunter AI navbar add korechi.

Input Box: Khub choto kore upore rekhechi, jate main focus Table e thake.

Table View:

SL: Serial number add kora hoyeche.

Link: Company namer pashe choto тЖЧ icon ache, click korle job post e niye jabe.

Status: Color code kora hoyeche (Applied=Blue, Interview=Yellow).

Details Modal: "Details" button chaple sundor ekta popup ashbe jekhane tumi sob field dekhte parbe. Ekhane dropdown ache status change korar jonno (Logic ta pore backend e add korbo).

Ei code ta paste kore save koro, tarpor dekho UI ta kemon lage! Kono change lagle bolbe. ЁЯЪА

bondhu scheme ta typescript use kore eto jotil apatoto ekhuni korte chacchi na

