yes tumi kichuta bujhe gecho ami chai eki sathe link photo text kaj korbe paspasi kichu special keyword thakbe jmn ekta dile ami ki ki job apply korchi sob chole asbe all jobs abr jodi ajker sudhu boli date wise ajker ta asbe sudhu emn ki ki feature add kora jay

Darun idea bondhu! Tumi chaccho bot ta ke just ekta "Saver" na rekhe ekta "Full Assistant" banate. Jeta tomar kotha shunbe ar uttor dibe.

Telegram bot diye eigula kora 100% somvob ar user experience er jonno eta sera hobe.

ЁЯУЛ Feature List (Master Plan)
Tomar chawa onujayi amra ei feature gula add korte pari:

1. Input Power (Ja tumi chaile):

ЁЯУ╕ Screenshot: Phone theke jober screenshot pathale se auto-extract kore save korbe (Website er moto).

ЁЯФЧ Link: Link dile ZenRows diye data anbe.

ЁЯУЭ Text: Copy-paste text nibe.

2. Smart Commands (Magic Keywords): Bot kichu nirdisto command chinbe. Jemon:

/myjobs ba "All Jobs": Shes 10 ta save kora job er list dekhabe (Title + Company + Status).

/today ba "Today": Ajke saradine ki ki job save korecho tar list dibe.

/stats ba "Summary": Ekta overview dibe (Ex: "Total 50 Applied, 2 Interviews, 1 Offer").

/search google: "Google" name kono job save kora ache kina khuje ber korbe.

3. Interactive Actions (Future Upgrade):

Job list er niche choto Button thakbe (Edit Status).

Chat er moddhei button e click kore status "Applied" theke "Interview" kora jabe.

ЁЯЫая╕П Technical Plan: Eita kivabe kaj korbe?
Amader api/telegram/route.js file ta ektu boro hobe. Logic ta hobe erokom:

Check Message Type:

Jodi photo hoy -> Image Process koro.

Jodi text hoy -> Niche jao.

Check Commands (Switch Case):

Jodi text /start hoy -> Welcome message.

Jodi text /today hoy -> Database query koro: createdAt = Today.

Jodi text /myjobs hoy -> Database query: find().sort(-1).limit(10).

Jodi onno kichu hoy -> Job Extract & Save koro.

Bondhu, tumi jodi raji thako, tahole amra 2 ta dhape kaj ta sesh kori:

Dhap 1: Age Image/Screenshot feature ta add kori (karon mobile user der jonno eta most important).

Dhap 2: Tarpor Keyword/Command system ta banabo (/today, /myjobs).

Kon ta age korbo bolo? Screenshot naki Command? ЁЯдФ

