Thik ache bondhu! Tomar dashboard er idea ta darun. Amra ekta Modern Sidebar Layout banabo jeta dekhte ekdom professional hobe.

Amra 4 ta File banabo/update korbo:

Layout (layout.js): Bam pashe Sidebar ar dan pashe Content thakbe.

