ржПржЦржи TrackButton ржХржорзНржкрзЛржирзЗржирзНржЯржЯрж┐ ржарж┐ржХржорждрзЛ ржХрж╛ржЬ ржХрж░рж╛рж░ ржХржерж╛ред ржЖржмрж╛рж░ ржЪрзЗрж╖рзНржЯрж╛ ржХрж░рзЗ ржжрзЗржЦрзЛ! ЁЯЪА

Bondhu, tomar idea ta darun! Tobe database er userEmail take array kora ta thik hobe na. Karon chinta koro:

Dhoro, User A ar User B duijonei same job track korche.

User A interview call pelo, tai se status update korlo "Interview".

Jodi amra eki job document share kori, tahole User B er status o auto "Interview" hoye jabe! Kintu User B hoyto reject hoyeche ba ekhono apply koreni.

Tai sobcheye valo solution holo: Cloning (Copy) kora. Jokhoni keu "Add to my track" click korbe, amra oi job er details (Title, Company, Link) niye notun ekta job create korbo oi user er jonno. Tahole sobay nijer moto kore status update korte parbe.

Ami 2ta dhap e kajta kore dicchi:

TrackButton Component: Ekta Client Component banabo jeta login check korbe ar job copy korbe.

Job Details Page Update: Notun button ar mailto: feature add korbo.

Dhap 1: Notun Component (src/components/TrackButton.js) ЁЯЦ▒я╕П
Eita notun file banate hobe.

Dhap 2: Public Job Page Update (src/app/jobs/[id]/page.js) ЁЯУД
Ekhane amra:

TrackButton ta import kore boshabo.

Contact User button e mailto: add korbo.

Ki ki change holo:

Send Message: Button e click korle ekhon default mail app open hobe.

Track This Job: Notun button add hoyeche. Click korle:

Login na thakle: Login page e niye jabe.

Login thakle: Job ta copy kore tomar dashboard e add kore dibe.

Try kore dekho! ЁЯЪА

